{"tid":1429643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察總部上月爆手足口病　數名警員中招","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:06:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ceab986e1b59f8c94cb8d6380790dd9d60d149e7","tid":1429643,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"網上討論區今日(7日)流傳一篇疑似警務人員談及近兩個月處理「暴亂」的文章，當中提到不少前線人員「長期唔夠瞓，近排好多人病」，文中更指「警察總部更加爆發手足口病」，原因是「大家打緊仗，冇人會考慮儀態，通地瞓，通地食。衞生自然變差」。 <br />\n<br />\n警方發言人回覆證實，警察總部於7月下旬有數名警務人員確診手足口病，相關人員現正休假或已復工。為確保其他人員免受感染，管方已經按指引於相關地方進行徹底清潔和消毒。不過衞生署就指，衞生防護中心暫時未有接獲有關呈報。"},{"pid":"f399ff5fcec54fe713babdfc894c7859d1399bcf","tid":1429643,"uid":52358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"錫佢春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591018028250bb88dfae2a655c73ed54694d3e62","tid":1429643,"uid":209464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"禽畜係麻煩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3748e98991753d15f9e799895d7cc73bfb9d6049","tid":1429643,"uid":21501,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1U3JXJj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1U3JXJj.png&h=fd5bcbaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃大仙擊殺！ </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf5fc76b7ae9f9f3aa6c22a4c72bd817c49c30a","tid":1429643,"uid":251292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"原來係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9402ad45ddd71600b43cbcd35eba3b865d36bdf5","tid":1429643,"uid":